Class FlipFitAdmin

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitUser
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitAdmin
public class FlipFitAdmin extends FlipFitUser
Represents an admin user in the FlipFit system, extending FlipFitUser. This class provides a default constructor initializing admin details.
